com.groovyclouds.aws
Class S3Grant

java.lang.Object
  com.groovyclouds.aws.S3Grant

class S3Grant

S3Grant encapsulates the grants for S3 bucket and objects. This class is used in set and get of grants. See S3 documentation for more details.
